Clone the repo on your terminal by typing "git clone https://github.com/ThiruLoki/PondyMail.git" 
Navigate to PondyMail directory
Change the permission by typing "chmod +x pondyMail.py
Replace the execution command into your own command 
Type "nano pondyMail.py"
Replace the value of COMMAND variable by your own command. by default it has "ipconfig" which gives the ip address of the host machine.
Replace EMAIL & PASSWORD variable into your own.
Replace server.sendmail (EMAIL, EMAIL, message + output) into from address & to address.
save the changes and run by typing "python pondyMail.py"
